title: Genius Quiz Premium v2.0
description:
Challenge your friend to see who is faster and smarter in this 100 questions game. Use your brain to get as far as you can in this game. 

Your reasoning ability is measured in every situation. There will be no instruction, every decision will be part of the Challenge Module. A mistake can be a big time waste in the advanced levels.

Premium Features:

-6 lifes
-Help at question 51 (don't need 3 lives to pass)
-No ads displaying

Features:
